text: Mulakuddu is a village in Bheemunipatnam mandal of Visakhapatnam district in the Indian state of Andhra Pradesh. It lies 37 km towards the north of Visakhapatnam City. == Demographics == The total population of Mulakuddu village is 4513 according to the 2011 Census of India. Among them males are 2255 and females are 2258 == References == Category:Villages in Visakhapatnam district
title: Mulakuddu
